    public abstract class PatchedJobIntentService
extends androidx.core.app.JobIntentService
    Workaround for JobIntentService crash bug
    PS! In order to keep the issue at bay never extend JobIntentService directly but rather given class extension instead!
    See Also:
    https://github.com/evernote/android-job/issues/255, https://medium.com/@eng.zak/workaround-to-solve-securityexception-caused-by-jobintentservice-1f4b0e688a26
